features: New Nonstick Technology - VINCHEF NON-STICK Frying Pans works with new micro-convex grain technology. The interior of this cookware uses micro-convex grain technology to resist sticking and shoveling, effectively improving durability and cooking performance. VINCHEF cookware made form high-quality stainless steel with a laser-etched non-stick surface using micro-convex grain technology to provide ideal hybrid cooking performance.

Non-Toxic and PFOA-Free - The VINCHEF 13 Inch Frying Pan and Lid are completely non-toxic and PFOA-free. With high-quality stainless steel, VINCHEF cookware is highly durable, corrosion-resistant, and does not react with food to ensure healthy cooking. Our cookware are dedicated to giving you and your family a healthier lifestyle.

For All Stove - The VINCHEF cookware is suitable for all stove. Our non stick frying pan works on all cook stove tops, include induction, gas, electric, halogen, glass, and ceramic. This non stick skillet combining the best features of a paella pan and a frying pan. Our frying pan has many uses. Frying and roasting can be mastered with ease. In addition to cooking seafood, it can also be used to make pancakes, barbecues, vegetables and so on.

Easy to Clean - Our wok pan is easy to clean. Just wipe it with a paper towel or rinse it with water, which make cooking not only easier but also more enjoyable. Additionally with high quality stainless steels and the aluminum core make our skillet is dishwasher-safe(Hand-washing is Recommended) and oven-safe up to 356°F.

About Service - Each frying pan has a strict quality control procedure If you have any problems about VINCHEF cookware, please feel free to contact us. Our service team will do the best to resolve it. We wish that you will have a good shopping experience from Amazon.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is worth to have in the kitchen
reviews.reviewText: I finally found a stainless steel pan that delivers the cooking experience that I have been seeking for. The pan is light weight, cooks well, washes well. I use the pant to cook or bake almost anything from stir frying food, frying, broiling, baking, and boiling.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Really love the height and how quickly it heats up. Been a really good pan a little heavy but I love how it cooks up meats

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Love the size and the loop handles
reviews.reviewText: I would give it five stars but I have only used it three times. First time after seasoning the skillet made hashbrowns and they stuck to the pan.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Best skillet! Nothing sticks and very easy to clean.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 13 inch paella pan
reviews.reviewText: I needed a 13 inch pan to cook and transport chicken pot pies and regular pies easier. This pan is perfect with handles and a lid. No more wrapping foil around the top and easy carry handles.My only negative is I kept cutting my hand on one of the handles when I noticed the handle was damaged. It had slithers of metal on the inside of the handle. I took a metal file to it and finally got it smoothed out. Since I got it from Amazon warehouse I knew there could be defects. I am not going to send it back because I think I have solved the problem but I do feel it was too pricey for the damage and problems it could have caused. Otherwise I love the product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars This is not non-stick
reviews.reviewText: This is a beautiful pan and it's the ideal size but sadly, it is definitely NOT non-stick. So far, almost everything I've sauteed in it has stuck. :( Dishes wish juice in them did not stick.
